{"tid":1740580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【圍堵中共】順便幫一幫推新疆人權法，推己及人","createTime":"2019-11-20T03:43:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T09:45:17.000Z","uid":12185,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"daf54c4f8b88af6e663187f0e2034f27f3ea588a","tid":1740580,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:43:37.000Z","msg":"我地法案岩岩過參議院，但今年仲有<strong>兩條</strong>新疆人權法案<br />\n香港有高度國際關注搶先過左，但唔好忘記有同我地同行嘅東突厥斯坦手足<br />\n兩條法案分別係<br />\n- Uyghur Human Rights Policy Act of 2019 (House Resolution H.R. 649 and Senate Resolution S. 178) <br />\n- UIGHUR Act of 2019 (House Resolution H.R 1025) <br />\n唔知係咪俾香港搶風頭，兩條法案仲早過香港人權法引入但都係仲未過眾議院<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n行動建議：<br />\n<a href=\"https://uhrp.org/what-you-can-do\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fuhrp.org%2Fwhat-you-can-do&d=qnfk3FWFLoR313jZLhvcNrhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=b485fcac\" target=\"_blank\">https://uhrp.org/what-you-can-do</a><br />\n入去睇吓有咩可以做，例如幫手寫信去國會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n通過埋呢兩條法案，香港就同新疆一齊成為美國喺新冷戰時期圍堵中國嘅兩座橋頭堡！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6313a7b47f6ab0a0edaf6ba2ab36f507a4b11c91","tid":1740580,"uid":228955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:44:55.000Z","msg":"yes"},{"pid":"5088f3b5616a87daf1377faf433a17dc62f896a8","tid":1740580,"uid":289259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"daf54c4f8b88af6e663187f0e2034f27f3ea588a","tid":1740580,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:43:37.000Z","msg":"我地法案岩岩過參議院，但今年仲有<strong>兩條</strong>新疆人權法案<br />\n香港有高度國際關注搶先過左，但唔好忘記有同我地同行嘅東突厥斯坦手足<br />\n兩條法案分別係<br />\n- Uyghur Human Rights Policy Act of 2019 (House Resolution H.R. 649 and Senate Resolution S. 178) <br />\n- UIGHUR Act of 2019 (House Resolution H.R 1025) <br />\n唔知係咪俾香港搶風頭，兩條法案仲早過香港人權法引入但都係仲未過眾議院<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n行動建議：<br />\n<a href=\"https://uhrp.org/what-you-can-do\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fuhrp.org%2Fwhat-you-can-do&d=qnfk3FWFLoR313jZLhvcNrhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=b485fcac\" target=\"_blank\">https://uhrp.org/what-you-can-do</a><br />\n入去睇吓有咩可以做，例如幫手寫信去國會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n通過埋呢兩條法案，香港就同新疆一齊成為美國喺新冷戰時期圍堵中國嘅兩座橋頭堡！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:45:32.000Z","msg":"各位手足，關於送林奠去大灣區的partition，尋日激增20000幾人(差不多簽署人數的10%)!，證明大家都好希望將佢舉家永遠封印晌大灣區！<br />\n<br />\n嘅然係咁就唔好停了，跟據早前民意調查有7成人唔妥佢嘅，咁我地嘅目標係咪應該set晌490萬個簽名呢？<br />\n<br />\n小弟英文唔好，如果可以的話，亦希望各手足可以幫手將佢推上國際！<br />\n<br />\n唔使俾錢架，簽完再share就唔使比錢㗎啦。<span style=\"color: red;\">最新消息：今朝22萬9千了！目標：490萬</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/uk-home-office-uk-home-office-should-revoke-carrie-lam-s-family-citizenship?cs_tk=AtIXNHLitQ7NOzo40F0AAXicyyvNyQEABF8BvKv03Ej5HuubaSSmIizKZKU%3D&amp;utm_campaign=514ad83a9aaf489a936c80aa7705b65d&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_source=recruit_sign_digest&amp;utm_term=cs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fuk-home-office-uk-home-office-should-revoke-carrie-lam-s-family-citizenship%3Fcs_tk%3DAtIXNHLitQ7NOzo40F0AAXicyyvNyQEABF8BvKv03Ej5HuubaSSmIizKZKU%253D%26utm_campaign%3D514ad83a9aaf489a936c80aa7705b65d%26utm_medium%3Demail%26utm_source%3Drecruit_sign_digest%26utm_term%3Dcs&d=qnfk3FWFLoR313jZLhvcNrhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=8d445f9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/uk-home-office-uk-home-office-should-revoke-carrie-lam-s-family-citizenship?cs_tk=AtIXNHLitQ7NOzo40F0AAXicyyvNyQEABF8BvKv03Ej5HuubaSSmIizKZKU%3D&amp;utm_campaign=514ad83a9aaf489a936c80aa7705b65d&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_source=recruit_sign_digest&amp;utm_term=cs</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hs8wPcW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumb